room_title: Escape room "Murder in the Morgue" by Escape It Newark in Columbus
room_description: Carlos was found dead, stabbed multiple times. The police say the killer was looking for something that Carlos had. When Dr. Martin Rossi, medical examiner, arrived at the crime scene he secretly found what the killer had been looking for. Now, Dr. Rossi has been found stabbed to death in the morgue. Can you solve the intent behind these murders or will you be next?
